import { combineReducers } from "redux"

import { getAllCandidates, getCandidateById, addCandidate, updateCandidate, removedCandidate, } from './CandidateReducer'
import { getAllSkill, addSkill, updateSkill, removedSkill, } from './SkillsReducer'
import { getAllSource, addSource, updateSource, removedSource, } from './SourceReducer'

export const MainReducer = combineReducers({
    getAllCandidates, getCandidateById, addCandidate, updateCandidate, removedCandidate,
    getAllSkill, addSkill, updateSkill, removedSkill,
    getAllSource, addSource, updateSource, removedSource,
})
